description:
Ever wanted to eat the same exact chili dog that sonic the hedgehog from sonic underground eats? Well now yu can, bitches! Because I know the recipe, and I'm sharing it with the word. Now go out an make some mean chili dogs, enjoy, and think of sonic underground everytime you take a big juicy bite ;)

Things you will need,
Hot dogs
Hot dog buns
chili sauce from dollar general
shredded yellow cheese
Mustard(optional)
